item.title: CVE-2022-45052|2024-10-16T11:52:25.281Z -- axiell -- iguana
item.description: A Local File Inclusion vulnerability has been found in Axiell Iguana CMS. Due to insufficient neutralisation of user input on the url parameter on the Proxy.type.php endpoint, external users are capable of accessing files on the server.
